            <input type="radio" name="item_a_6" value="5">
            Died <strong>(Complete Notification of Death Form)</strong>
        </div>
        <div>
            <input type="radio" name="item_a_6" value="6">
            Other
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="formlabel">
        7. Did site report incident to the participant:
